Proyek Uni - Pemograman Mobile



Novel Reader

Reading novels is a common hobby for a lot of people, one that is done a lot on mobile devices. The most common form of reading a novel offline uses an .epub file reader, but most reader applications can only read downloaded files.
With this app I want to allow for users to read novels from existing local saves but also to allow for progress saves, like bookmarking.



Status Proyek
pertama proyek memiliki semua rerquirement, agar mudah belajar proyek dibuat dengan memastikan semua requirement berfungsi dalam screen-screen sendiri

Setelah semua sudah berfungsi / di approve, proyek akan diupdate agar resemble sebuah applikasi.

